for lube?

07:38.457 --> 07:40.751
Welcome to the War Room.
Here's the plan.

07:40.834 --> 07:42.002
This is you and I.

07:42.086 --> 07:43.879
At daybreak, we take
your tank --

07:43.963 --> 07:45.631
uh, that's represented
by a butter dish --

07:45.714 --> 07:49.093
and we head to By Golly Gulch
and rescue Ted.

07:49.176 --> 07:51.887
