And... this isn't to scale.

07:51.971 --> 07:53.806
It's, uh...
it's for butter.

07:53.889 --> 07:55.057
Where's By Golly Gulch?

07:55.140 --> 07:57.601
I can't find it.
This map is overly complicated.

07:57.685 --> 07:59.478
It's three Thomas guides
taped together.

07:59.561 --> 08:01.021
I'll just use my vphone.

08:01.105 --> 08:02.773
[cellphone beeps]
Um, Vphone!

08:02.856 --> 08:04.984
Directions to By Golly Gulch.

08:05.067 --> 08:07.069
