08:59.830 --> 09:02.082
[ rumbling ]

09:02.166 --> 09:04.209
[ crowd screaming ]

09:06.045 --> 09:07.713
Nobody move, see!

09:07.796 --> 09:11.508
This is kind of a holdup!
We are insane criminals!

09:11.592 --> 09:14.803
