obsessively insane,

10:49.898 --> 10:51.358
and we demand a Guild
representative

10:51.441 --> 10:53.443
to take us
to Dunwitch Asylum.

10:53.527 --> 10:55.237
Hey, Ricky, these two
are G.C.l.

10:55.320 --> 10:57.030
and bound for wacky world.

10:57.114 --> 10:58.407
I'll radio it in.

10:58.490 --> 11:00.242
[chuckles]
Less work for us, huh?

11:00.325 --> 11:01.827
All right, you two, let's go.

11:01.910 --> 11:03.704
What? W-We're insane
criminals, too!

11:03.787 --> 11:05.664
