silent.

11:07.791 --> 11:09.084
[fluorescent lights buzzing ]

11:09.168 --> 11:11.170
[clock ticking ]

11:13.672 --> 11:15.591
She, uh, she really
loves you, you know.

11:15.674 --> 11:17.342
Uh... okay.

11:17.426 --> 11:20.345
Yeah. I love you.
We all love you.

11:20.429 --> 11:21.889
Uh... neat.

11:21.972 --> 11:24.016
[buzzer]
15 minutes.

11:24.099 --> 11:26.852
My little jelly bean!

11:26.935 --> 11:30.230
Mom!
